The '''National Herbarium''' at [[Peradeniya]], near [[Kandy]] in the Central province of [[Sri Lanka]], was started in about 1821 by Alexander Moon, who was the director of the [[Royal Botanical Gardens, Peradeniya|Botanical Gardens]] there.{{r|hist|hist2}}

